[[File:Bundle Starter Bundle.png|thumb|A image of the "Starter Bundle".]]
'''Bundles & Packs''' is how content gets delivered to users. Users can receive bundles from VRC+, [[Events|events]], code redemptions, or globally given out by VRChat.

== Overview ==
Bundles & Packs can be found in the "Bundles & Packs" [[Inventory|inventory]] tab. Users must claim the bundle or pack to recieve its contents. Content that can be awarded includes any content type the inventory supports, excluding Photos, Prints, User Icons, UI Themes & Backgrounds.

If a user has multiple bundles or packs in their inventory, they can choose which one they want to open by clicking the arrow on either side of the menu.

Bundles & Packs can have an expiry date, in which users must claim before a certain date.

